          "label": "The solution is withheld until sufficient pressure has been built \u2014 tension is not released by pivoting to the proposed work too early"
        },
        {
          "id": "inevitable_arrival",
          "label": "By the time the proposed work is introduced, it feels like the only logical response rather than one of several possible approaches"
        }
      ],
      "priority": 1
    },
